Package: restic-backup
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, restic, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Unified restic backup (systemd + logrotate)
 Installs a systemd oneshot service + timer to run nightly restic backups,
 per-host include/exclude, and a Prometheus freshness metric via node_exporter.
